Package org.drasyl.channel

netty Channel for the drasyl overlay network.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChannelDirectPathChanged
    Signals that the path to the remote peer has been changed from direct to relayed or vice versa.
    ConnectionHandshakeChannelInitializer  
    DrasylChannel
    A virtual Channel for peer communication.
    DrasylServerChannel
    A virtual ServerChannel used for overlay network management.
    InetAddressedMessage<M>
    A message that wraps another message with an InetSocketAddress.
    OverlayAddressedMessage<M>
    A message that wraps another message with a DrasylAddress.
    RelayOnlyDrasylServerChannelInitializer
    A ChannelInitializer for DrasylServerChannels that relays all messages through super peers.
    TraversingDrasylServerChannelInitializer
    A ChannelInitializer for DrasylServerChannels that tries to traverse (if any) NATs with a fallback to relaying all messages through super peers.
